{"tid":1726732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好就咁笑鳩啲老解出黎執垃圾就算","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:13:21.000Z","uid":33959,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae0c9f7038becb2468eb1582ec3a5382e51b485","tid":1726732,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:58:35.000Z","msg":"「中央人民政府負責管理香港特別行政區的防務。<br />\n香港特別行政區政府負責維持香港特別行政區的社會治安。<br />\n中央人民政府派駐香港特別行政區負責防務的軍隊不干預香港特別行政區的地方事務。香港特別行政區政府在必要時，可向中央人民政府請求駐軍協助維持社會治安和救助災害。<br />\n駐軍人員除須遵守全國性的法律外，還須遵守香港特別行政區的法律。」<br />\n<br />\n你話我太敏感又好乜都好，自發就可以咁光明正大走出黎？同埋14條都寫到明，要特區政府請求先可以出黎行動，而家算係點？<br />\n當然我唔係叫手足郁佢地，但點都唔可以俾佢溫水煮蛙咁笑下笑下就越出越多<br />\n就算未必有用都好，一定要上twitter煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0366db3df8b41a82c04e781eb31e4a80e9452c","tid":1726732,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:59:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"444350f9fabf6fa898f2abaab58b22745c267bb6","tid":1726732,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"115d68095fa76961d7728055222bcd823ceb9557","tid":1726732,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c9e652be58cebac1ebd53fa8f28236af9d9aff5d","tid":1726732,"uid":183499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"無錯，從來都無「自發」呢回事！唔可以變常態同溫水煮蛙"},{"pid":"2a6b43e642303a12c28a4405fda5839a1ddb57da","tid":1726732,"uid":52621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府打算出老解了</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba014a6e42f5dbf6d8fc2e9525b837a52b64836d","tid":1726732,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:04:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"cca9652baeb4592a070affd3de5e4467c1788fb